description: The ChunkedFileToken contains data to track the chunked upload a file.  The first step in uploading a file is to create ChunkedFileToken.

key.description: The S3 key for this object.  Synapse will provide this value upon creation.

uploadId.description: The unique ID that tracks this file upload. Synapse will provide this value upon creation.

fileName.description: The short name of the file.  This should include the appropriate file prefix.

contentType.description: The content type of the file. Must be: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_media_type

contentMD5.description: The file's content MD5 (should be a HEX encoded string).
